FBIS4-42441 "drweu107_j_94009" FBIS-WEU-94-107 Daily Report 2 Jun 1994 ITALY & VATICAN CITY Coalition Wins Chair of RAI Watchdog Group Coalition Wins Chair of RAI Watchdog Group LD0206203994 Rome RAI Due Television Network in Italian 1745 GMT 2 Jun 94 LD0206203994 Rome RAI Due Television Network Italian BFN [Text] There is a piece of good news for the ruling coalition. A short time ago, Marco Taradash, a Radical Party deputy who ran on a Forza Italia electoral list, was elected chairman of the parliamentary watchdog committee on RAI. He obtained 22 votes, besting the challenge of the left-wing candidate, Mauro Paisan.
